    "This undoubtedly brings additional computing costs.",
    "Therefore, the development of end-to-end networks, or more easily integrated network modules, is also a valuable direction.",
    "While ensuring the effectiveness of the method, real-time processing of massive point cloud data is an urgent problem for deep learning point cloud registration methods.",
    "If you want the solution to be real-time, as well as data processing in large-scale scenarios, you have to consider the support of computer hardware and software.",
    "In future work, more excellent performance of GPU and its running conditions, and more efficient method structure are undoubtedly the focus of attention of researchers."
